    <string name="blood_test_source">Zdroj: Bergamaschi MM, Karschner EL, Goodwin RS, Scheidweiler KB, Hirvonen J, Queiroz RH, Huestis MA. Impact of prolonged cannabinoid excretion in chronic daily cannabis smokers\' blood on per se drugged driving laws. Clin Chem. 2013;59(3):519-526. doi:10.1373/clinchem.2012.195503. PMID: 23449702; PMCID: PMC3717350.</string>
