    <string name="hair_test_source">Zdroj: Taylor M, Lees R, Henderson G, Lingford-Hughes A, Macleod J, Sullivan J, Hickman M. Comparison of cannabinoids in hair with self-reported cannabis consumption in heavy, light and non-cannabis users. Drug Alcohol Rev. 2017;36(2):220-226. doi:10.1111/dar.12412. Epub 2016 Jun 14. PMID: 27296783; PMCID: PMC5396143.</string>
